SUMMARY:SCENE QUEEN (UK) (Uhrzeit prüfen)
LOCATION:Chelsea
DESCRIPTION:Doors: 19:30h\, Show: 20h   “Put a knife up to his boner\, cut him” with those nine words a trend was born and Scene Queen (along with the genre name she coined\, “Bimbocore”) was introduced to the world. Fast forward a year later\, Scene Queen has taken over the world and the Bimbocore movement continues to grow.  With her debut album\, Hot Singles In Your Area\, Scene Queen hopes to expound on the idea of reclaiming your sexuality\, confidence\, and feeling empowered to express your true self regardless of what anyone will think. While Scene Queen has become a divisive and polarizing figure that is the embodiment of female empowerment and sexual freedom\; she has built a reputation as someone who holds herself to no boundaries or genre. Leading the scene in pink high heel boots and mini-skirts in a black t-shirt world\, she’s as comfortable writing songs about cutting off mysogyny’s manhood as she is screaming obscenities about everyday frustrations into metal breakdowns that quake inside your soul. While Hot Singles In Your Area tells the story of Scene Queen coming into her own and enjoying being single\, young\, and free\, the album reflects a broader meaning as well. The album explores and pays homage to the early internet era as well as all the sex workers who have laid the foundation for Bimbocore to exist. Scene Queen adds\,“The album is about having fun with yourself while reclaiming your sexuality.” As an outspoken advocate for LGBTQIAA rights and a fearless crusader against misogyny\, body-shaming\, and sex-shaming\, Scene Queen proves that you can name every song after a different category of pornography and be valiantly sex-positive while doing a two-step into a metal/hardcore breakdown. Bimbocore forever.  https://scenequeenrocks.com    Tickets: www.oeticket.com/event/21609384?affiliate=MT5
URL:https://www.chelsea.co.at/concerts.php#concert_6705
END:VEVENT
